      <title>日本央行預計通膨將維持在目標附近，暗示升息機會</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/boj-project-inflation-will-stay-around-target-signal-chance-rate-hike-2024-04-22/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本央行預計將在周五發布的新預測中預測未來三年通膨率將保持在 2% 的目標附近，這表明日本央行準備今年從目前接近零的水平再次升息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/boj-project-inflation-will-stay-around-target-signal-chance-rate-hike-2024-04-22/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 10:40:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>收入較低的美國消費者面臨貸款壓力，而銀行則縮減開支</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/us-consumers-lower-incomes-face-loan-stress-while-banks-pull-back-2024-04-22/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根據最近的數據和銀行高層的數據，美國收入較低的借款人越來越難以償還貸款，這促使銀行在發放信用卡和汽車貸款時變得更加謹慎。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/us-consumers-lower-incomes-face-loan-stress-while-banks-pull-back-2024-04-22/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 10:37:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
